reviewText: Just so so . Not too interesting.

This is so amazing. I popped this DVD in and I was blown away at how it brought me back to my childhood. I remember watching these shows as a little kid at my grandmothers house. Probably some of my favorite quotes of all time came from this movie. While watching, I was transported to my former child self sitting 5 inches away from the set laughing my head off. Definitely a wonderful buy.
